## SLIDE 9 — Security Features

### 1. JWT Authentication
```
Login → Server issues Token (7 days valid)
Every API request → Token verify hota hai
Invalid token → 401 Unauthorized
```

### 2. Razorpay HMAC-SHA256 Verification
```
Payment complete → Razorpay sends signature
Backend → signature verify karta hai
✅ Valid → Order DB mein save hota hai
❌ Invalid → Order reject — no fraud possible
```

### 3. Rate Limiting (DDoS Protection)
| Route | Limit |
|---|---|
| Login / Signup | 10 req / 15 min |
| Payment | 5 req / 10 min |
| General API | 100 req / 15 min |
| Product Browse | 200 req / 15 min |

### 4. Admin-Only Routes
- `adminOnly` middleware — non-admins get 403 Forbidden
- Banned users blocked at login level

