## SLIDE 10 — AI Recommendation System (70:30 Algorithm)

### Formula
```
Final Score = 0.70 × Popularity Score
            + 0.30 × Discovery Score
```

### Popularity Score (70%) — Jo bik raha hai
| Factor | Weight |
|---|---|
| Orders in last 30 days | 40% |
| Average review rating | 25% |
| Unique buyers count | 20% |
| Revenue generated | 15% |

### Discovery Score (30%) — Jo nayi / unsold hai
| Factor | Weight |
|---|---|
| Days since last order (inverted) | 40% |
| Price vs category average | 30% |
| Profile completeness | 20% |
| Artisan join recency | 10% |

### Why 70:30?
- **70% popular** → User ko quality products mile → Trust bane
- **30% discovery** → New artisans ko exposure mile → Platform grow kare

### Caching
- Results **RAM mein 30 minutes** ke liye cache hote hain
- Order place hone pe cache automatically delete hota hai
- Performance: 99% requests bina DB query ke serve hoti hain

