## SLIDE 13 — Challenges Faced & Solutions

| Challenge | Solution |
|---|---|
| Express route order bug (`/my` caught by `/:id`) | Specific routes pehle define kiye |
| Razorpay payment fraud prevention | HMAC-SHA256 server-side verification |
| Existing products no status field | `$or` query with `$exists` check |
| Heavy recommendation DB queries | node-cache with 30 min TTL |
| Mobile responsiveness | CSS media queries, bottom tab bar |
| DDoS protection | express-rate-limit with tiered limits |

